{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Dreamlike Love with Seira</strong></i> is a light visual novel, featuring renowned illustrator rubisama as the director and original artist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This visual novel presents a single linear story, with text dialogue, manga-style illustrations, 2D character art, and voice acting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It does not include branching storylines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2764Hope you could experience the sweet service and warm dreams with Seira within the brief durations\u2764</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planning, Artist:Rubi-sama (\u308b\u3073\u69d8)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scenario: Orisuke (\u30aa\u30ea\u30b9\u30b1)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986260/extras/Story.jpg?t=1730705557\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Story about Sweet Dream</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist, Haruto Watari, finishes a stressful day of work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">He goes back home, exhausted, to a cluttered room that only makes him all the more fatigued.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But unable to find the drive or will to clean up, he collapses into bed and falls asleep.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Then, he has an unbelievable dream... A dream where he's the owner of a luxurious Western mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And in that dream mansion, he meets a maid named Seira.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A maid whose duty is to serve him, her master\u2014</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be it brewing a delicious cup of black tea or comforting him with kind swords, she heals his tired soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dream of sweet, passionate service is about to begin...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986260/extras/Character.jpg?t=1730705557\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Maid Providing Perfect Service</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2615\ufe0f Seira \u2615\ufe0f</strong> <strong><i>Voice Actress: Hana Kagehotaru</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986260/extras/seira.jpg?t=1730705557\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Miss Seira, the maid who appears in Haruto's dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With proper etiquette and versatile domestic skills, she excels at brewing exquisite black tea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">She patiently listens to Haruto's work-related complaints, embodying a truly perfect woman.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot; Please don't hesitate. After all, you are the owner of this mansion.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our discord</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986260/extras/discord.jpg?t=1730705557\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome my master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986260/b632cd6a46a706e3c0f53d980dd176e08dfba6f6.jpg"},{"name":"Afternoon tea with master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986260/b8403a35bb23b446c4a488d35df4b29a55c0db29.jpg"},{"name":"What next to dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986260/1